{
  "texts": [
    "The training and test parts of this ranking procedure are carried out independently.",
    "The total of the test and training phase scores determines the final score.",
    "Table 7 presents a comprehensive overview of the score analysis, while Fig. 21 presents a radar map that illustrates the outcomes.",
    "Upon analyzing the table and figure, XGB and DT were the two best models throughout training, with scores of 103 and 90, respectively.",
    "Their performance decreased during the test phase with XGB scoring 98 and DT scoring 88."
  ]
}